Package shared.proxy.games

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CreateGameRequest
    Information sent to the server to request that a new game be created
    EmptyPlayer
    Used in creating a NewGame, contains no information
    Game
    Simple representation of a game used in displaying available games
    JoinGameRequest
    A request sent to the server to join a specific game
    LoadGameRequest
    Requests that a saved game be loaded from a file
    NewGame
    Returned after creating a game.
    Player
    Representation of a player used for listing available games.
    SaveGameRequest
    Used primarily for debugging purposes, saves the state of the game to a file
